  <jpcrp_cor:NotesRegardingPromissoryNotesDueOnBalanceSheetDateTextBlock contextRef="Prior1YearInstant">
&lt;div style="margin-left: 9.0pt"&gt;※８  連結会計年度末日満期手形&lt;/div&gt;
